title: Microsoft's OpenAI Investment Could Face EU Probe
description: The EU is considering whether to launch a review of Microsoft’s investment in ChatGPT maker OpenAI under the bloc’s merger regulations, a month after the U.K. said it was also considering whether the tech partnership could have an impact on competition.
